title: Thor - Vikings
description:
In the year 1003 AD, Harald Jaekelsson and his band of Vikings raided the town of Lakstad, on the west coast of Norway. Having killed all the men and children, and having their way with the women, then killing them as well, they begin to leave for the New World. But the town wise man, thought dead, places a curse on them. "Though you sail for a thousand years, O Norsemen," says the old man, "You shall not reach the land you seek." After sailing the seas for 1000 years, then they finally land in New York. They begin killing everyone in site, and are about to have a little fun with a woman, when Thor shows up.
